metadata.name: Many Hands #1
metadata.description:
Many Hands is a generative set of 5,000 NFTs created using Virtual Reality that exists on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each NFT is created from 7 unique layers painted immersively with VR goggles. Through Compassion International, 100% of the proceeds will finance full-ride university scholarships and ongoing support for 32 high-achieving students in Haiti to pursue a 4-year university program.

Visit https://www.manyhandsnft.com/ to learn more.
